-Comelec commissioners be appointed by independent process to be nonpartisan
-return party-list system to original intent to represent marginalized groups
-pass anti-political dynasty law

legacy.full_text:
2022 PH Election - Bacolod City

In a tight race, BBM flipped Bacolod, winning by 3%

2016: Leni 54% - BBM 19%
2020: BBM - 44% - Leni 40%

BBM gained ~78k votes while Leni lost ~7k voters. The total vote count increased by ~58k from 2016 (Congressional canvass data)

#Halalan2022 https://t.co/DMBbDNqTV4

legacy.full_text:
2022 PH Election - Cagayan de Oro

In 2016, BBM narrowly won CDO by just 1% in a 3-way race (BBM 30 Leni 29 Cayetano 28)

In 2022, BBM won with 77% share adding over 164k votes. Leni went from ~70k in 2016 to 34k in 2022. 

Total votes increased by 68k votes in CDO.

#Halalan2022 https://t.co/FxMoIvphAK
